\begin_layout Subsection
幂级数解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Frobenius 方法
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
假设在方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的解在方程的有限远常点或正则奇点 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

 附近可以展开为幂级数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x)=\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s}\left[a_{0}+a_{1}\left(x-x_{0}\right)+a_{2}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{2}+\cdots\right]=\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s+i}\quad a_{0}\ne0
\]

\end_inset

根据有限远常点或正则奇点的定义，
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

 也应当可以在点 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

 附近展开为幂级数：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
P(x)=\sum_{j=-1}^{\infty}p_{j}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{j}\qquad Q(x)=\sum_{k=-2}^{\infty}q_{k}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{k}
\]

\end_inset

将这三个幂级数代入方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}0 & =\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(s+i)(s+i-1)\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s+i-2}\\
 & +\sum_{j=-1}^{\infty}p_{j}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{j}\times\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(s+i)\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s+i-1}\\
 & +\sum_{k=-2}^{\infty}q_{k}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{k}\times\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s+i}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

合并 
\begin_inset Formula $(x-x_{0})$
\end_inset

 的同幂次项，再令各项系数为 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

，得到一组关于 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ a_{i}\right\} _{i=0}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

 的恒等式。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由「最低次项 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s-2}$
\end_inset

 的系数为 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

」得到的恒等式
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
s(s-1)+p_{-1}s+q_{-2}=0\label{eq:指标方程}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

被称作
\emph on
指标方程
\emph default
 (indicial equation)，其中 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{-1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $q_{-2}$
\end_inset

 均为已知系数，因此它是一个关于 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 的一元二次方程。对于数学物理中常见的二阶线性常微分方程，这两个解通常都是实数。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由「次低次项 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s-1}$
\end_inset

 的系数为 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

」得到的恒等式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{1}(s+1)s+p_{-1}a_{1}(s+1)+p_{0}a_{0}s+q_{-2}a_{1}+q_{-1}a_{0}=0
\]

\end_inset

可以用指标方程简化为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
a_{1}(2s+p_{-1})+a_{0}(p_{0}s+q_{-1})=0\label{eq:次低次项对应的恒等式}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

当 
\begin_inset Formula $2s+p_{-1}\ne0$
\end_inset

 时，
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 有唯一确定的值；反之，
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 的值不定，通常可以取为 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
由「后续各项（即 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(x-x_{0}\right)^{s+n}$
\end_inset

 其中 
\begin_inset Formula $n=0,1,2,\dots$
\end_inset

）系数为 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

」得到的恒等式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{n+2}(s+n+2)(s+n+1)+\sum_{j=-1}^{n+1}p_{j}a_{n+1-j}(s+n+1-j)+\sum_{k=-2}^{n}q_{k}a_{n-k}=0
\]

\end_inset

经过整理，可以改写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}a_{n+2} & =-\frac{\sum_{j=0}^{n+1}p_{j}a_{n+1-j}(s+n+1-j)+\sum_{k=-1}^{n}q_{k}a_{n-k}}{(s+n+2)(s+n+1+p_{-1})+q_{-2}}\\
 & =:f(a_{0},a_{1},\dots,a_{n},a_{n+1})
\end{aligned}
\label{eq:递推关系}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

这是一个用已知系数表示未知系数的
\emph on
递推关系
\emph default
 (recurrence relation)。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Fuchs 定理
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "sec:Fuchs定理"

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[Fuchs]
\end_layout

\end_inset

在方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的
\emph on
常点
\emph default
或
\emph on
正则奇点
\emph default
附近，Frobenius 方法
\emph on
至少
\emph default
可以给出一个幂级数形式的解。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
如果指标方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:指标方程"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的两个解 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{2}$
\end_inset

 满足
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
(s_{1}-s_{2})\notin\mathbb{Z}
\]

\end_inset

则 Frobenius 方法可以在方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的常点或正则奇点 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

 附近给出两个线性无关的幂级数解
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}u_{1}(x) & =(x-x_{0})^{s_{1}}\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(x-x_{0})^{i}\qquad a_{0}\ne0\\
u_{2}(x) & =(x-x_{0})^{s_{2}}\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}b_{k}(x-x_{0})^{k}\qquad b_{0}\ne0
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark*
以上定理没有否认 Frobenius 方法在 
\begin_inset Formula $(s_{1}-s_{2})\in\mathbb{Z}$
\end_inset

 时给出两个线性无关解的可能性。下一小节就给出了这样一个示例。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
简谐方程在 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}=0$
\end_inset

 附近的解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将幂级数形式的解
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x)=\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}x^{s+i}\quad a_{0}\ne0
\]

\end_inset

代入简谐方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u''+\omega^{2}u=0\qquad\omega\ne0
\]

\end_inset

得到指标方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
s(s-1)=0\implies s=0,1
\]

\end_inset

和递推关系
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
a_{n+2}=\frac{-\omega^{2}}{(s+n+2)(s+n+1)}a_{n}\qquad n=0,1,2,\dots\label{eq:简谐函数的系数递推关系}
\end{equation}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若 
\begin_inset Formula $s=0$
\end_inset

，则恒等式
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:次低次项对应的恒等式"

\end_inset

变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{1}(2s+p_{-1})+a_{0}(p_{0}s+q_{-1})=0\implies a_{1}\cdot0=0
\]

\end_inset

此时 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 可以取任意值。由递推关系
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:简谐函数的系数递推关系"

\end_inset

可以得到两组独立的系数
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{2n}=\frac{(-1)^{n}\omega^{2n}}{(2n)!}a_{0}\qquad a_{2n+1}=\frac{(-1)^{n}\omega^{2n+1}}{(2n+1)!}\frac{a_{1}}{\omega}\qquad n=0,1,2,\dots
\]

\end_inset

于是，方程的解可以表示为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}u(x) & =\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}a_{2n}x^{2n}+\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}a_{2n+1}x^{2n+1}\\
 & =a_{0}\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{(-1)^{n}(\omega x)^{2n}}{(2n)!}+\frac{a_{1}}{\omega}\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{(-1)^{n}(\omega x)^{2n+1}}{(2n+1)!}\\
 & =a_{0}\cos\omega x+\frac{a_{1}}{\omega}\sin\omega x
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{0}$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 为待定参数，由边界条件确定。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
若 
\begin_inset Formula $s=1$
\end_inset

，则恒等式
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:次低次项对应的恒等式"

\end_inset

变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{1}(2s+p_{-1})+a_{0}(p_{0}s+q_{-1})=0\implies a_{1}\cdot2=0
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $a_{1}$
\end_inset

 必须为 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

。由递推关系
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:简谐函数的系数递推关系"

\end_inset

可以得到两组独立的系数
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
a_{2n}=\frac{(-1)^{n}\omega^{2n+1}}{(2n+1)!}\frac{a_{0}}{\omega}\qquad a_{2n+1}=0\qquad n=0,1,2,\dots
\]

\end_inset

于是，方程的解可以表示为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u(x)=\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}a_{2n}x^{2n+1}=\frac{a_{0}}{\omega}\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{(-1)^{n}(\omega x)^{2n+1}}{(2n+1)!}=\frac{a_{0}}{\omega}\sin\omega x
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{0}$
\end_inset

 为待定参数，由边界条件确定。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
综上，通过 Frobenius 方法可以得到简谐方程的两个线性无关解：
\begin_inset Formula $\cos\omega x$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $\sin\omega x$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
第二解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
Wronskian
\end_layout

\begin_layout Definition
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

[Wronskian]
\end_layout

\end_inset

对于 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个至少 
\begin_inset Formula $(n-1)$
\end_inset

 阶可导的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u_{i}(x)\right\} _{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

，称以下行列式为它们的 Wronskian
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{12\cdots n}(x):=\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{llll}
u_{1} & u_{2} & \cdots & u_{n}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & \cdots & u_{n}'\\
\cdots & \cdots & \cdots & \cdots\\
u_{1}^{(n-1)} & u_{2}^{(n-1)} & \cdots & u_{n}^{(n-1)}
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
对于 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 个至少 
\begin_inset Formula $(n-1)$
\end_inset

 阶可导的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u_{i}(x)\right\} _{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

，如果它们的 Wronskian 不恒为零，则它们线性无关；否则，它们线性相关。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ k_{i}\right\} _{i=1}^{n}$
\end_inset

 的线性代数方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{bmatrix}\begin{array}{llll}
u_{1} & u_{2} & \cdots & u_{n}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & \cdots & u_{n}'\\
\cdots & \cdots & \cdots & \cdots\\
u_{1}^{(n-1)} & u_{2}^{(n-1)} & \cdots & u_{n}^{(n-1)}
\end{array}\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}k_{1}\\
k_{2}\\
\cdots\\
k_{n}
\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}0\\
0\\
\cdots\\
0
\end{bmatrix}
\]

\end_inset

有非零解 
\begin_inset Formula $\iff$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $W_{12\cdots n}(x)\equiv0$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
二阶线性齐次常微分方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

至多有两个线性无关解：
\begin_inset Formula $u_{1}(x)$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{2}(x)$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Proof
假设方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

有三个线性无关解 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ u_{i}(x)\right\} _{i=1}^{3}$
\end_inset

，它们的 Wronskian 为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{12\cdots n}=\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{lll}
u_{1} & u_{2} & u_{3}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & u_{3}'\\
u_{1}'' & u_{2}'' & u_{3}''
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}=-u_{1}'W_{23}'+u_{2}'W_{13}'-u_{3}'W_{12}'
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{ik}':=\dv{x}\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{ll}
u_{i} & u_{k}\\
u_{i}' & u_{k}'
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}=\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{ll}
u_{i} & u_{k}\\
u_{i}'' & u_{k}''
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}\qquad i,k=1,2,3
\]

\end_inset

同时，由方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

可知
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{u_{i}''}{u_{i}}+P\frac{u_{i}'}{u_{i}}=-Q=\frac{u_{k}''}{u_{k}}+P\frac{u_{k}'}{u_{k}}\qquad i,k=1,2,3
\]

\end_inset

两端同乘 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{i}u_{k}$
\end_inset

 并移项，可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{i}u_{k}''-u_{k}u_{i}''+P\cdot\left(u_{i}u_{k}'-u_{k}u_{i}'\right)=0\qquad i,k=1,2,3
\]

\end_inset

从而有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{ik}'=-P\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{ll}
u_{i} & u_{k}\\
u_{i}' & u_{k}'
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}=-P\cdot W_{ik}\qquad i,k=1,2,3
\]

\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}W(x;u_{1},u_{2},u_{3}) & =-u_{1}'P\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{ll}
u_{2} & u_{3}\\
u_{2}' & u_{3}'
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}+u_{2}'P\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{ll}
u_{1} & u_{3}\\
u_{1}' & u_{3}'
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}-u_{3}'P\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{ll}
u_{1} & u_{2}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}'
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}\\
 & =P\begin{vmatrix}\begin{array}{lll}
u_{1} & u_{2} & u_{3}\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & u_{3}'\\
u_{1}' & u_{2}' & u_{3}'
\end{array}\end{vmatrix}\equiv0
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

这与假设矛盾。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
积分形式的第二解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
假设已经获得了方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:二阶线性齐次ODE首项系数为一"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

的一个解 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{1}$
\end_inset

，并且存在另一个与之线性无关的解 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{2}$
\end_inset

，则由
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{12}'=-P\cdot W_{12}\implies\frac{\dd{W_{12}}}{W_{12}}=-P\dd{x}
\]

\end_inset

可以推出（省略 
\begin_inset Formula $W$
\end_inset

 的下标）
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\ln\frac{W(x)}{W(a)}=\implies W(x)=W(a)\exp\left(-\int_{a}^{x}P(\xi)\dd{\xi}\right)
\]

\end_inset

考虑到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W(x)=u_{1}u_{2}'-u_{2}u_{1}'=u_{1}^{2}\dv{x}\frac{u_{2}}{u_{1}}
\]

\end_inset

于是有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dv{x}\frac{u_{2}}{u_{1}}=W(a)u_{1}^{-2}\exp\left(-\int_{a}^{x}P(\xi)\dd{\xi}\right)
\]

\end_inset

直接积分可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{2}(x)=u_{1}(x)W(a)\int_{b}^{x}u_{1}^{-2}(\eta)\exp\left(-\int_{a}^{\eta}P(\xi)\dd{\xi}\right)\dd{\eta}
\]

\end_inset

通过引入适当的系数，总是可以令 
\begin_inset Formula $W(a)=1$
\end_inset

，于是第二解的一般形式（积分下限可以省略）可以表示为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
u_{2}(x)=u_{1}(x)\int^{x}u_{1}^{-2}(\eta)\exp\left(-\int^{\eta}P(\xi)\dd{\xi}\right)\dd{\eta}\label{eq:积分形式的第二解}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

如果恰好有 
\begin_inset Formula $P(x)\equiv0$
\end_inset

，则第二解的一般形式可以简化为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{2}(x)=u_{1}(x)\int^{x}u_{1}^{-2}(\eta)\dd{\eta}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Remark*
以上积分形式的第二解通常只具有理论意义，实际计算往往难以实施，需要用其他方法寻找第二解。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsubsection
幂级数解形式的第二解
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
按照 Frobenius 方法中的步骤，可以得到指标方程
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:指标方程"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

。将它的两个解记为 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}=\sigma$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{2}=\sigma-n$
\end_inset

，代回指标方程可以得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
p_{-1}-1=n-2\sigma
\]

\end_inset

不失一般性，下面只考虑 
\begin_inset Formula $n\in\mathbb{N}_{+}$
\end_inset

 的情形。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
根据
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "sec:Fuchs定理"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $s_{1}=\sigma$
\end_inset

 所对应的幂级数解
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{1}(x)=(x-x_{0})^{\sigma}\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(x-x_{0})^{i}
\]

\end_inset

总是可以通过 Frobenius 方法得到。将它和 
\begin_inset Formula $P(x)$
\end_inset

 的幂级数展开式代入积分形式的第二解
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:积分形式的第二解"

\end_inset

，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{2}(x)=u_{1}(x)\cdot\int_{b}^{x}\frac{\exp\left(-\int_{a}^{\eta}\sum_{j=-1}^{\infty}p_{j}\left(\xi-x_{0}\right)^{j}\dd{\xi}\right)}{(\eta-x_{0})^{2\sigma}\left(\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(\eta-x_{0})^{i}\right)^{2}}\dd{\eta}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
先考虑指数函数项中的积分
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{a}^{\eta}\sum_{j=-1}^{\infty}p_{j}\left(\xi-x_{0}\right)^{j}\dd{\xi}=p_{-1}\ln\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)+\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\frac{p_{j}}{j+1}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j+1}+C_{a}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{a}$
\end_inset

 是与积分下限 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 有关的积分常数。于是指数函数项可以整理为幂级数形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned} & \exp\left(-\int_{a}^{\eta}\sum_{j=-1}^{\infty}p_{j}\left(\xi-x_{0}\right)^{j}\dd{\xi}\right)\\
= & (\eta-x_{0})^{-p_{-1}}\cdot\exp\left(-\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\frac{p_{j}}{j+1}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j+1}\right)\cdot\exp(-C_{a})\\
= & \frac{1-\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\frac{p_{j}}{j+1}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j+1}+\left(-\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}\frac{p_{j}}{j+1}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j+1}\right)^{2}+\cdots}{(\eta-x_{0})^{n+1-2\sigma}E_{a}}\\
= & \frac{\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}b_{j}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{n+1-2\sigma}}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

这里利用了 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{-1}-1=n-2\sigma$
\end_inset

，指数函数的 Taylor 展开式 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp x=\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\frac{x^{k}}{k!}$
\end_inset

，将常数 
\begin_inset Formula $\exp(C_{a})$
\end_inset

 表示为 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{a}$
\end_inset

 并将其吸收进幂级数的系数 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ b_{j}\right\} _{j=0}^{\infty}$
\end_inset

 中。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
再考虑被积函数的分母，对其作 Taylor 展开得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\frac{1}{(\eta-x_{0})^{2\sigma}\left(\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(\eta-x_{0})^{i}\right)^{2}} & =\frac{1}{(\eta-x_{0})^{2\sigma}\left(1+\sum_{i=1}^{\infty}a_{i}(\eta-x_{0})^{i}\right)^{2}}\\
 & =\frac{\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\binom{-2}{k}\left(\sum_{i=1}^{\infty}a_{i}(\eta-x_{0})^{i}\right)^{k}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{2\sigma}}\\
 & =\frac{\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}c_{k}(\eta-x_{0})^{k}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{2\sigma}}
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

这里利用了幂函数的 Taylor 展开式 
\begin_inset Formula $(1+x)^{\alpha}=\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\binom{\alpha}{k}x^{k}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将以上两个结果代回到第二解的表达式中，得到
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}u_{2}(x)= & u_{1}(x)\cdot\int_{b}^{x}\frac{\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}b_{j}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{n+1-2\sigma}}\cdot\frac{\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}c_{k}(\eta-x_{0})^{k}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{2\sigma}}\dd{\eta}\\
= & u_{1}(x)\cdot\int_{b}^{x}\frac{\sum_{j=0}^{\infty}d_{j}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{n+1}}\dd{\eta}\\
= & u_{1}(x)\cdot\int_{b}^{x}\frac{d_{n}}{\eta-x_{0}}\dd{\eta}\\
+ & u_{1}(x)\cdot\int_{b}^{x}\frac{\sum_{j=0}^{n-1}d_{j}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j}+\sum_{j=n+1}^{\infty}d_{j}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j}}{(\eta-x_{0})^{n+1}}\dd{\eta}\\
= & u_{1}(x)\cdot d_{n}\ln\abs{x-x_{0}}+C_{b}\\
+ & u_{1}(x)\cdot\left(\sum_{j=0}^{n-1}\frac{d_{j}}{j-n}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j-n}+\sum_{j=n+1}^{\infty}\frac{d_{j}}{j-n}\left(\eta-x_{0}\right)^{j-n}\right)
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{b}$
\end_inset

 是与积分下限 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

 有关的积分常数。考虑到 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{1}(x)=\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}a_{i}(x-x_{0})^{i+\sigma}$
\end_inset

，最后一行的幂级数应当从 
\begin_inset Formula $(x-x_{0})^{\sigma-n}$
\end_inset

 项开始。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
综上，对应于 
\begin_inset Formula $s_{2}=\sigma-n$
\end_inset

 的第二解应当具有以下形式
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
u_{2}(x)=u_{1}(x)\cdot\ln\abs{x-x_{0}}+(x-x_{0})^{s_{2}}\sum_{i=0}^{\infty}b_{i}(x-x_{0})^{i}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

